#重置样式
```
body{font:12px Arial,"Hiragino Sans GB","微软雅黑","黑体-简",Helvetica,sans-serif; color:#4c4d4d; background:#ecf0f1;}
body,div,p,span,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,ul,ol,li,dl,dt,dd,pre,form,tr,td,th,table{box-sizing:border-box; border:0px; padding:0px; margin:0px;}
img,a img{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0px;} 
h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{box-sizing:border-box; font-size:12px; font-weight:normal;}
ul,li,ol,dt,dl,dd{box-sizing:border-box; list-style:none;}
address,cite,code,em,th,i{box-sizing:border-box; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;}
table{ box-sizing:border-box; border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}
label,input,textarea,select,button{box-sizing:border-box; font-family:Arial,"Hiragino Sans GB","微软雅黑","黑体-简"; margin:0px; padding:0px; vertical-align:middle; outline:none;}
input,button,select,img{ box-sizing:border-box; line-height:normal;}
a{box-sizing:border-box;  color:#4c4d4d;text-decoration:none; outline: none;}
a:hover{box-sizing:border-box;  color:#e76f12; text-decoration:none; }
a:active{ box-sizing:border-box; outline: none; star:expression(this.onFocus=this.blur());}
```

#移动端屏幕适配相关代码
```
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
```

#JS执行屏幕rem计算
```
htmlFontSize();/**开始进入界面执行方法***/
window.onresize = function() {
	htmlFontSize();/**屏幕变化时执行方法***/
}

function htmlFontSize() {
	var w = document.documentElement.clientWidth;
	var i = parseInt(w) / 768;
	document.documentElement.style.fontSize = (parseInt(w) / 768) * 40 + "px";
}
```
